name: qdrant-php (hkulekci)
description: [项目级] Qdrant is a vector similarity engine & vector database. It deploys as an API service providing search for the nearest high-dimensional vectors. With Qdrant, embeddings or neural network encoders can be turned into full-fledged applications for matching, searching, recommending, and much more!。来源: https://github.com/hkulekci/qdrant-php

genes.title: 项目概述
genes.content:
Qdrant is a vector similarity engine & vector database. It deploys as an API service providing search for the nearest high-dimensional vectors. With Qdrant, embeddings or neural network encoders can be turned into full-fledged applications for matching, searching, recommending, and much more!

来源: https://github.com/hkulekci/qdrant-php
语言: PHP
